id: act1_03_consent

prompt:
  A technician walks you into a small room. A consent form fills the wall in
  six paragraphs. At the bottom: "I understand that the experience adapts to
  my behaviour."

choice c_sign_kindly:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Sign, smile at the technician, and tell her you trust her not to push too hard.
  evidence: signed the consent and asked the technician for gentleness

choice c_sign_after_reading:
  tendency: control
  text: Read every paragraph aloud, ask which clauses are negotiable, and then sign.
  evidence: cross-examined every clause of the consent form before signing

choice c_sign_under_protest:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Sign, but write "under protest" beside your name.
  evidence: signed the consent under written protest
